This App explores the concept of reducing the uncertainty of casual-carpooling. Most of the time, riders wait in line without ever really knowing if they'll be getting a ride, and drivers may wait at pickup locations for riders without really knowing if there are any riders coming. 

Features to be implemented include:
- Using geolocation to detect whether a rider/driver is still available

- Proximity based notifications to riders/drivers for spontaneous carpool matching (i.e, breaking free of the constraints of designated pickup locations